import InputGroup from 'react-bootstrap/InputGroup';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import { Row,Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';

function Clients() {
  return (
    <>
    <Container>
    <Row className='my-5'>
      <Col>
      <Form.Label htmlFor="CompanyName">Company Name:</Form.Label>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Name" id="CompanyName" />
      </Col>
      </Row>
      <Row className='mb-2'>
        <Col>
        <Form.Label htmlFor="CompanyName">Company Adresse:</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" className='mb-2' />
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" />
      </Col>
      </Row>
      <Row gl={1} className='mb-2'>
        <Col>
      <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" />
      </Col>
      </Row>
      <Row className='mb-2'>
        <Col>
      <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" />
      </Col>
      </Row>
      <Row className='mb-2'>
        <Col>
      <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" />
      </Col>
      </Row>
      </Container>

    </>
  );
}

export default Clients;
